# FILE: adminDashboard/inventoryTerminal/storeStockManager.desc
# ROLE: Physical-to-Digital Stock Synchronization Engine
# ROUTE: /admin/inventory
# ACCOUNT: Admin only (Vendor business accounts submit items for approval here too)
# THEME: Dark · spreadsheet-style · low-stock alerts

## 1. LIVE INVENTORY MATRIX
- STYLE: compact table · border-[#1E2D45] · alternating row bg
- COLUMNS:
  - Product ID: e.g., "HS-LTP-01" — monospace
  - Name: "ThinkPad T480 — مجدد"
  - Stock Count: integer · rose text when ≤ 2 (low stock alert)
  - Price: SYP
  - Discount Tag: 🎓 طالب (shows applied student discount %)
  - Source: 🏠 منصة / 🤝 وسيط (vendor name if business account)
- LOGIC: stock === 0 → status becomes "نفد المخزون" automatically

## 2. VENDOR PRODUCT APPROVAL QUEUE
- Separate section: products submitted by businessType === 'vendor'
- STATUS: 🕒 قيد المراجعة · ✅ منشور · ❌ مرفوض
- ACTIONS: [✅ قبول ونشر] [❌ رفض مع سبب]

## 3. STOREFRONT VISIBILITY TOGGLE
- Per product: [👁️ ظاهر في المتجر] | [🔒 مخفي]
- Allows preparing new products before publishing

## 4. CATEGORY & TAG MANAGEMENT
- Groups: 💻 إلكترونيات · 📐 أدوات هندسية · 📚 قرطاسية
- Must match filter sidebar in /store exactly

## 5. RESERVED COUNTER
- Shows how many units are "reserved" (receipt uploaded but not confirmed)
- Auto-releases back to stock if admin rejects the receipt in revenue tracker

## 6. BULK PRICING
- [💹 تعديل الأسعار العامة] — adjust all prices by % (handles SYP fluctuations)

## 7. ACTIONS
- [➕ إضافة منتج جديد] — opens form with image upload field (Cloudinary/Imgur)
- [📄 تصدير تقرير المخزون (PDF)]
- MANTRA: "الدقة هي الاحترافية — Challenge Every Day."
